{"type": "article", "id": 13053, "title": "像“大白”的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-05T07:00:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000234uQzjADgU6CvLNBMO.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t如今“大白”当道，“暖洋洋”气质人人都爱质。德国设计师 Konstantin Grcic 最近为意大利家具品牌 Magis 设计了一款看上去非常宽厚敦实的椅子，它有着一个超级大的圆柱形的弧形扶手和靠背，舒适又安全。流畅的线条让它看上去又像是一个巨大的棉花糖，暖暖甜甜的。白色那一款，正切面看起来还真有点儿像是大白呢。最后送上<a href=\"http://konstantin-grcic.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261407126SIqzEcH2avltfRD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140712HdifeCtPGz9hR8Nw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140713lArgjSexG2Q6ZJHU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261407135UqH8I2JOXgsdbMo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140714lo9peR5IqLBtr2Vu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140714WqrVP6LgXRl3Ea0b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}